# publish the under-declaring vendor (no descriptor) so producer and local can resolve it as a managed dependency
> vendor/publishLocal
# producer declares the library vendor needs but does not; the declaration exports into producer's own descriptor
> checkExport
# the consumer resolves producer (and transitively vendor) and folds the propagated requirement; the unresolvable library fails the link
-> consumer/Compile/snxLink
# local declares the library for its OWN link; the declaration folds into that link, where the unresolvable library fails it
-> local/Compile/snxLink
